io.sphere.sdk.products.commands.updateactions

Class SetTaxCategory

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.sphere.sdk.models.Base
      • io.sphere.sdk.commands.UpdateActionImpl<Product>
        • io.sphere.sdk.products.commands.updateactions.SetTaxCategory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UpdateAction<Product>

    public final class SetTaxCategory
extends UpdateActionImpl<Product>
    Adds, changes or removes a product's tax category. This change can never be staged and is thus immediately visible in published products.

    See also ProductUpdateCommand.

    TaxCategoryFixtures.withTransientTaxCategory(client(), taxCategory ->
        withUpdateableProduct(client(), product -> {
            assertThat(product.getTaxCategory()).isNotEqualTo(taxCategory);
            final ProductUpdateCommand command = ProductUpdateCommand.of(product, SetTaxCategory.of(taxCategory.toResourceIdentifier()));
            final Product updatedProduct = client().executeBlocking(command);
            assertThat(updatedProduct.getTaxCategory()).isEqualTo(taxCategory.toReference());
            return updatedProduct;
        })
);

    See the test code.
